            <a class="get_it" href="https://www.github.com/mirumee/satchless">Download source</a>
            <p class="hint"><strong>Warning:</strong> Currently Satchless is in an early stage of development. It is already possible to build a shop on top of it, but still you should be prepared for radical and backward-incompatible changes to the code.</p>
        </div>
